'''硒酸钍'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为Th(SeO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，存在八水合物<ref>G. Wyroubov. The Selenate of Thorium. ''Paris. Z. Kryst. Min.'', 1910. 47. 371-372. CAN4: 10278.</ref>及碱式盐<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=54|issue=6|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2015-03-16|pages=3022–3030|doi=10.1021/acs.inorgchem.5b00133|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.inorgchem.5b00133|title=Chemical and Structural Evolution in the Th–SeO 3 2– /SeO 4 2– System: from Simple Selenites to Cluster-Based Selenate Compounds|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=Bin Xiao, Eike Langer, Jakob Dellen, Hartmut Schlenz, Dirk Bosbach, Evgeny V. Suleimanov, Evgeny V. Alekseev}}</ref>。
==物理性质==
硒酸钍是具有放射性的固体，微溶于水，溶解度为0.5 g。<ref name=hxhg />
